Willie STEWART, Administrator of the Estate of Virgil Stewart, Deceased, v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 1337. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit Oct. 8, 1935. William A. Tidwell, of Idabel, Okl., for appellant. C. W. Miller, Asst. U. S. Atty., of Muskogee, Okl., for the United States.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed, for failure to prosecute.
